==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɔː(r)də(r)|-ɔː(r)də(r)]]
====Homophones====
*[[boarder]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#The [[outer]] [[edge]] of something.
#A [[decorative]] [[strip]] around the edge of something.
#A strip of [[ground]] in which [[ornamental]] [[plant]]s are [[grown]].
#The [[line]] or [[frontier]] [[area]] [[separating]] [[political]] or [[geographical]] [[region]]s.

====Translations====
*German: [[Grenze]] {{f}} (1,4)

===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

#''(transitive)'' To put a border on something.
#''(transitive)'' To [[lie]] on, or [[adjacent]] to a border.

====Translations====
